        "timestamp": "2019-06-18 23:31:08.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nThe changes are required as Multus making the assumption that both the pod and network crd without namespace will be in the same namespace. User deployment has to explicitly refer \"default\" namespace. NPWG Spec and code in Multus doesn't explain this nature very well. Multus maintainer has captured the issue here - https://github.com/intel/multus-cni/issues/337.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
